<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">

 <head>

  <title>CSS Reftest Reference</title>
  <link rel="author" title="Ian Hickson" href="mailto:ian@hixie.ch"/>

  <style type="text/css"><![CDATA[
  p {margin: 0px;}

  div {color: navy; font-size: 4em; margin: 0.25em;}

  span.Times {font-family: "Times New Roman";}
  
  span.Arial {font-family: Arial;}
  
  span.CourierNew {font-family: "Courier New";}

  ]]></style>

 </head>

 <body>

  <p>In each of the three lines below, the two words should look identical.</p>

  <div><span  class="Times">&#x0162;&#x0119;&#x015F;&#x0163;</span>  &mdash; <span  class="Times">&#x0162;&#x0119;&#x015F;&#x0163;</span></div>

  <div><span  class="Arial">&#x0162;&#x0119;&#x015F;&#x0163;</span>  &mdash; <span  class="Arial">&#x0162;&#x0119;&#x015F;&#x0163;</span></div>

  <div><span  class="CourierNew">&#x0162;&#x0119;&#x015F;&#x0163;</span>  &mdash; <span  class="CourierNew">&#x0162;&#x0119;&#x015F;&#x0163;</span></div>

 </body>
</html>